Variability . Length ♂♂ 3.74–4.27 mm , ♀♀ 3.98–4.61 mm . This species shows variability in the size and shape of the dorsal black tomentous elytral macula. This macula can be somewhat reduced, apparently longitudinally elongate, especially in specimens from North Africa (described as
C. schoenherri ssp. laportei
).
